OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777057867
OL,3,COfficers face misconduct probe over
OL,4,Ctheir role in investigation
OL,6,FTwo police officers are being
OL,7,Finvestigated for potential gross
OL,8,Fmisconduct for their roles in the case
OL,9,Fof Christopher Trybus who was cleared
OL,10,Fby a jury of the manslaughter of his
OL,11,Fwife.
OL,13,FThe 44-year-old was acquitted at
OL,14,FWinchester Crown Court in connection
OL,15,Fwith the death of 34-year-old Tarryn
OL,16,FBaird who took her own life at their
OL,17,Fhome in Swindon, Wiltshire, in
OL,18,FNovember 2017.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
