PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777057867
OL,3,COfficers face misconduct probe over
OL,4,Ctheir role in investigation
OL,6,FHe was also found not guilty of two
OL,7,Fcharges of rape against her and a
OL,8,Fcount of controlling and coercive
OL,9,Fbehaviour.
OL,11,FThe Independent Office For Police
OL,12,FConduct (IOPC) has now confirmed that
OL,13,Fit is investigating the actions of two
OL,14,Fofficers ` one who attended the house
OL,15,Fwhere Ms Baird died and another who
OL,16,Fwas involved in the investigation and
OL,17,Fhas since retired.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
