FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777057867
OL,3,COfficers face misconduct probe over
OL,4,Ctheir role in investigation
OL,6,FA spokesman said: "We received a
OL,7,Fvoluntary conduct referral from
OL,8,FWiltshire Police on 25 June 2025
OL,9,Frelating to its investigation into the
OL,10,Fdeath of Tarryn Baird who was found
OL,11,Fdead at her home on 28 November 2017.
OL,13,F"The police investigation concluded
OL,14,Fthere was insufficient evidence to
OL,15,Fcharge anyone in connection with her
OL,16,Fdeath and the case was closed.
OL,18,F"However, after a review by Dorset
OL,19,FPolice, charges were later brought.
OL,26,@nD@SOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777057867
OL,3,COfficers face misconduct probe over
OL,4,Ctheir role in investigation
OL,6,F"Our independent investigation is
OL,7,Fexamining Wiltshire Police's handling
OL,8,Fof the initial investigation to
OL,9,Festablish if there were potentially
OL,10,Fany missed opportunities to
OL,11,Finvestigate effectively.
OL,13,F"We are specifically considering the
OL,14,Factions of two officers, one who
OL,15,Fattended the scene where Ms Baird was
OL,16,Ffound dead and the other who was
OL,17,Finvolved in the investigation and has
OL,18,Fsince retired from the force.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777057867
OL,3,COfficers face misconduct probe over
OL,4,Ctheir role in investigation
OL,6,F"They are being investigated by us for
OL,7,Fpotential gross misconduct. Our
OL,8,Finquiries continue."
OL,10,FAssistant Chief Constable Liz Coles,
OL,11,Fof Wiltshire Police, said: "Our
OL,12,Fthoughts are with Tarryn Baird's
OL,13,Ffamily and friends at this time.
OL,15,F"Wiltshire Police investigated the
OL,16,Fcircumstances surrounding Tarryn's
OL,17,Fdeath in November 2017.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@TO]sD@\OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777057867
OL,3,COfficers face misconduct probe over
OL,4,Ctheir role in investigation
OL,6,F"As part of our inquiries, we made a
OL,7,Fmandatory referral to the Independent
OL,8,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) due
OL,9,Fto our previous contact with Tarryn.
OL,11,F"The IOPC conducted an independent
OL,12,Finvestigation which concluded in 2019
OL,13,Fand found Wiltshire Police had no case
OL,14,Fto answer.
OL,16,F"The same year, the criminal
OL,17,Finvestigation, then being undertaken
OL,18,Fby the Major Crime Investigation Team,
OL,19,Fconcluded that no further action was
OL,20,Fto be taken with regards to
OL,21,FChristopher Trybus.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777057867
OL,3,COfficers face misconduct probe over
OL,4,Ctheir role in investigation
OL,6,F"In 2020, evidence was identified
OL,7,Fwhich led to the criminal case being
OL,8,Fre-opened.
OL,10,F"Following a review, Assistant Chief
OL,11,FConstable Mark Cooper (now Deputy
OL,12,FChief Constable), requested an
OL,13,Findependent police force take over the
OL,14,Fcriminal investigation in 2021.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777057867
OL,3,COfficers face misconduct probe over
OL,4,Ctheir role in investigation
OL,6,F"Dorset Police agreed to do this in
OL,7,FDecember 2021 and subsequently, the
OL,8,FCrown Prosecution Service authorised
OL,9,Fcharging Christopher Trybus with
OL,10,Fmanslaughter, two counts of rape and
OL,11,Fengaging in controlling or coercive
OL,12,Fbehaviour.
OL,14,F"Wiltshire Police subsequently made a
OL,15,Fsecond referral into the IOPC
OL,16,Fregarding this case.
OL,18,F"As an independent investigation by
OL,19,Fthe IOPC is ongoing, it would not be
OL,20,Fappropriate for us to comment further
OL,21,Fat this time."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777057867
OL,3,COfficers face misconduct probe over
OL,4,Ctheir role in investigation
OL,6,FMr Trybus had been accused of carrying
OL,7,Fout a "tsunami" of violent and
OL,8,Fcontrolling domestic abuse against Ms
OL,9,FBaird which he denied.
OL,11,FAfter the initial police investigation
OL,12,Finto her death was closed, Ms Baird's
OL,13,Fmother, Michelle Baird, discovered her
OL,14,Fdaughter had kept photos of injuries
OL,15,Fshe had suffered on her phone -
OL,16,Fleading to a second police probe being
OL,17,Flaunched in October 2020.
OL,26,@oD@GOUoD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777057867
OL,3,COfficers face misconduct probe over
OL,4,Ctheir role in investigation
OL,6,FThe trial heard that Ms Baird was
OL,7,Fdiagnosed as probably suffering from
OL,8,Fpost traumatic stress disorder (PTSD)
OL,9,Fafter she witnessed violent car-
OL,10,Fjackings in South Africa where she and
OL,11,Fthe defendant grew up.
OL,13,FThe couple moved to the UK in 2007,
OL,14,Fand married in 2009, but an attempted
OL,15,Fburglary in 2015 appears to have
OL,16,Ftriggered Ms Baird's mental health
OL,17,Fissues including anxiety and
OL,18,Fdepression leading her to seek help
OL,19,Ffrom mental health professionals, the
OL,20,Fcourt heard.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777057867
OL,3,COfficers face misconduct probe over
OL,4,Ctheir role in investigation
OL,6,FSpeaking outside court, Mr Trybus
OL,7,Fsaid: "After three police
OL,8,Finvestigations over the course of 10
OL,9,Fyears, I'm relieved that the jury has
OL,10,Fcarefully considered the evidence and
OL,11,Freached the correct verdict today."
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
